metadata.description:
Collects Marvel Adventures Spider-Man (2010) #1-4.

To the public, he's a mystery. To the media, he's a menace. To the Torino crime family, he's a possible million dollar payday. To Gwen Stacy, he's the subject of her latest school paper, and a way to become a reporter for the Daily Bugle. He's Peter Parker, the amazing Spider-Man! Featuring SHANG-CHI, WOLVERINE & BULLSEYE!
metadata.name: Marvel Adventures Spider-Man
